text: This page has the List of caudillos of Panama A caudillo (diminutive of caput "head". Caudillo means "little head" or "little chief") is part of the larger Iberian tradition of authoritarian leaders == List of caudillos of Panama== * Juan Eligio Alzuru * José Domingo Espinar * Tomás de Herrera * José de Fábrega, "Liberator of the Isthmus" * Manuel Noriega * Omar Torrijos Category:Lists of people *
title: List of caudillos of Panama
